{"type": "article", "id": 26556, "title": "纸板收音机", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-09T06:56:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 91, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702150607JBIkL4nOdr30DvUS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">要说到能为社会带来帮助的好设计，<a href=\"http://www.shackletongroup.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Shackleton Group</a> 为智利的国家紧急情况办公室 ONEMI 设计的这款纸板型收音机就是其中的典范。作为一个地震多发的国家，这款收音机可以让民众在发生紧急情况时收听到消息。选用纸板这一材质不仅便于发放和携带，组装也比较容易。纸板的一面还装有一块太阳能板，用来为收音机提供电力。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150604kVXhqAdPlFCisZYE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150605omV9MGbhjSiYIJX4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150605h378qwfrBsPCFoOk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021506061nJezxshoaL50Dq2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}